et, if this is known, this is the only optional parameter needed (default: 0)\n\n    is_big_endian -- bool: what format string should be used for unpacking the size value (default: True)\n\n    number_of_bytes_for_size_prefix -- the number of bytes to read to determine the total size of the message to pass (default: 0)\n\n    size_value_includes_size_prefix_bytes -- bool: if size value includes the size_prefix_bytes based on the systems implementation\n\n    size_value_should_be_included_in_final_message  -- bool: if size value should be prepended to the byte sequence, likely only Husky logic wants this (default: False)\n\n    -----\n\n    get_bytes_from_socket(remote_socket=conn, number_of_bytes_to_read=100) - likely would not be called directly, in most cases\n\n    get_bytes_from_socket(remote_socket=conn, is_big_endian=True, number_of_bytes_for_size_prefix=4) - reads 4 bytes to get the size, then reads that amount (DCM socket, etc)\n\n    get_bytes_from_socket(remote_socket=conn, is_big_endian=False, number_of_bytes_for_size_prefix=2, should_remove_prefix_size_from_read=True) - reads 2 bytes to get the size,\n    then reads that calculated amount minus 2 (Husky socket, etc)"]}, {"name": "plantstar_shared.tcp_socket_utils.send_message_on_socket", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "remote_socket", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "dumpsable_object", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "plantstar_shared.tcp_socket_utils.send_encoded_message_on_socket", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "remote_socket", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "encoded_message", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "plantstar_shared.tcp_socket_utils.get_object_from_socket", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "remote_socket", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "number_of_bytes_to_read", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "is_big_endian", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "number_of_bytes_for_size_prefix", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "size_value_includes_size_prefix_bytes", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Function that is used between the APU and DCM to send dictionaries. Returns a tuple of the object and its size in bytes."]}], "variables": [{"name": "plantstar_shared.tcp_socket_utils.SIZE_OF_UNSIGNED_INT_FOR_HUSKY", "type": null, "documentation": ["size of the integer value that precedes data coming from Husky OIs"]}, {"name": "plantstar_shared.tcp_socket_utils.SIZE_OF_UNSIGNED_INT_STRUCT", "type": null, "documentation": ["size of the integer value that precedes data coming from most sockets (DeviceController, DCM, etc)"]}], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "plantstar_shared.DataCollectionModuleProcessNames", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "plantstar_shared.DataCollectionModuleProcessNames.DataCollectionModuleProcessNames", "bases": ["SysconType"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "plantstar_shared.DataCollectionModuleProcessNames.DataCollectionModuleProcessNames.DIGITAL_ANALOG_PROCESSOR_INTERFACE", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "plantstar_shared.DataCollectionModuleProcessNames.DataCollectionModuleProcessNames.DIGITAL_ANALOG_TASKER_INTERFACE", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "plantstar_shared.DataCollectionModuleProcessNames.DataCollectionModuleProcessNames.PROCESS_SPAWNER", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "plantstar_shared.DataCollectionModuleProcessNames.DataCollectionModuleProcessNames.RAW_DATA_PROCESSOR_INTERFACE", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "plantstar_shared.DataCollectionModuleProcessNames.DataCollectionModuleProcessNames.RTL_RIO_3", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "plantstar_shared.DataCollectionModuleProcessNames.DataCollectionModuleProcessNames.RTL_RIO_4", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variab